Hello, Haskell!
If I break, you can:
  1. Restart:           M-x haskell-process-restart
  2. Configure logging: C-h v haskell-process-log (useful for debugging)
  3. General config:    M-x customize-mode
  4. Hide these tips:   C-h v haskell-process-show-debug-tips
λ> Var "HELLO"
Var "HELLO"
λ> LInt 10
LInt 10
λ> parseExpr "1"
Left "=>" (line 1, column 1):
unexpected "1"
expecting identifier
λ> parseExpr "HELLO"
Right (Var "HELLO")
λ> parseExpr "owain"
Right (Var "owain")
λ> parseExpr "x"
Right (Var "x")
λ> parseExpr "owain"
Right (Var "owain")
λ> parseExpr "1"
Right (Lit (LInt 1))
λ> parseExpr "2"
Right (Lit (LInt 2))
λ> parseExpr "2 2 3"
Right (App (App (Lit (LInt 2)) (Lit (LInt 2))) (Lit (LInt 3)))
λ> parseExpr "\x -> x"
